Sometimes I wish I could read minds. Not like in the movie and know each and every thought the people have but, being able to have some hint, to ears some whisper from targeted people thought.
I would like to understand body language with a small extra mind reading.

I'm sure it would help me to understand the people that are around me and I'm interested in. I would understand quickly if I pissed off people around me, if the next joke I will do will be too much, I would know where and when to go or stay, would know if someone is interested in me or not and would not stuck around thinking I still have a chance (worst case that happen in high school ages ago)


This morning I saw that Garfield cartoon in the journal about John meeting his... I'll say "new girlfriend" for the first time and he was able to chat with her only on the phone. Too shy i guess. 
I found that funny because I was asking my self, why is it easier to write (chat) than speak when meeting someone?

I been fired... Again...

I'm getting sick of this. 
I was suppose to go see a friend, that live far from here, for her birthday and won't be able du to lack of money and stupid boss kicking me out. 

*Sigh*

Youu know, there is some time that you feel like something will go wrong about a situation or something you'll do. You donT' know why, but deep inside you, you know that whatever you do to get ready on time, something will come up and ruin everything. 

Well it happen to me friday night. I was doing everything possible to get my Red Car fixe but I felt like something would go wrong this weekend. Didn't know why, but it was like a feeling that was telling me, "STAY HOME" As usual, I just thought I was freaking out and ignore it. So I went to see my friend Crowraptorrr and when I get there I knew the badluck was starting. She wasn't at the meeting point. One of her tire blew out on the highway. Then when she finaly get to the meeting point, she was still a little sick. If it was only that, but no it didn't stop because I was feeling a little numb all weekend and my Red Car got tricky. Transmission was missing Oil so when it was getting hot, the speed was skipping or jumping or just not working at all. Because we took my car we had to spend Sunday morning to fins a mechanic that could help me to get that fix but on the one open a Sunday, no one had the part. "Dealership Problem" they say... So I end up using all the knowledge I accumulate with all the wreck I had in the past to buy some Transmission Oil and fill it up. Because I didn't want to get stuck on an American highway a Sunday just before Memorial Day (that mean everything close and loosing my job for not being able to be there before Tuesday) I had to left earlier than planed... 

Now, I need to wait a month before seeing her again. *sigh*

Yeah, Yeah, I know I don't post much thing in my journal. But right now I'm planing a road trip all around the USA.

I'll let you know how I'm doing into my journal on FA.
For now I have few step to do befor I go.

STEP Description Statur
Step 1 ; Get the date of my vacation Done (beguining of september)
Step 2 : Get my "passport" Pending
Step 3 : Get the money Done
Step 4 : Get my car Fixe Done (bought a new one)
Step 5 : to know where I'm going Pending (It's a road trip, I go south and that it....)


Now beside that, the only thing needed is some place to sleep... the way I'm planing this trip it's easy, I'm driving untill I get bored then I look for a nice place to visite. if I don't find any place to sleep? My car or motel room should be fine. I don't have much money, so mostly sleeping in my car.

I have enough money for food and gaz. if I need more money I'll look for some work to do to continue the trip. I go for 2 week. but I took a month of vacation just in case I like living in the US.

If anyone know a nice place to see or have some job to give me for one day or two feel free to tell me.
I know, I don't know many people in the US and I speak french with a medium english. but it not a reason to not make friend over there and get better in english.

Time on my side
I got it all
I've heard that pride
Always comes before a fall
There's a rumour goin' round the town
That you don't want me around
I can't shake off my city blues
Everyway I turn I lose

Love is like oxygen
You get too much you get too high
Not enough and you're gonna die
Love gets you high

there is few way to forget thing, Alcohol, drugs, gambling and speed on the highway. 

When you take drugs, you compleaitly  block signal in your head, so you're too stone to remember anything.

When you take alcohol, you partialy  block signal in your head, so you still can do the party.

When you do gambling, you lose a lot of money, so you think about the other problem.

When you go over the limit speed on the highway, you only think about the road in front of you, so if you think about something else you can die.


For me the only way to forget thing that hurt me os driving as fast as I can until I run out of gaz.
I know I could kill my self but I don't mind about it. Is the best way to die for me.

Today I realize that when I speak english, I'm more talk active with customer than my friend! What's the matter, I mean, hey are friend, so I'm not suppose to be affraid to talk to them. 

Maybe I'm just affraid they judge me for my english and push me away... I dunno... It just weird.

And a customer ask me what part of Europe I come from? Because I have an european accent in english. It's not the first time people ask me that question. Most of the time people ask me if I'm German and some time Russian.

I like raining day. Is the perfect day to stay home with your lover and listen an old movie or just be naked and run downtown. Ok maybe the second option is not realy good, but at least it's a funny thought ;) And for me the first option it can't be done. Working and have no lover for the moment :| So, I'm sad and bored...

I finally repair the keyboard that Aurora gave me. I cleaned it (was very dirty) and made a part of the circuit. Ok, the Caps Lock made some freegame when you push it, but I'll like to see you repair a "flex PCB". Normaly, a regulard PCB is made of fiberglass, but the flex one are a sheet of plastic with carbon line. So, you can't do any solder on it.

Anyway, it seem working good, I right this post with it.

Now, the only thing left to do, is putting some green LED under the key to light it up a bit!

I should write something here, but... I'm too lazy to do anything.

Oh, I get a new job. Technician on the road. I reapir TV now.
